"it will tell you. The most common issue is directory permissions; your "
"HTTP user needs write permissions to your whole ownCloud directory. (See "
":ref:`strong_perms_label`.) Another common issue is SELinux rules (see "
":ref:`selinux-config-label`.) Otherwise you will see messages about "
"checking your installation and making backups."
